<br>
The ability to take controll of your pet totaly, as in you enter its body and you are in controll.   We know from the Eye of Tallon line of spells that it is possible to controll a pets movements, dont know about actions. <br>
<br>
Probibly way overpowering but would be loads of fun. <p>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=112952</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nucci01>Nucci 01</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 7:11:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8338.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ability Idea - </span><hr size=1> Very cool idea, but they'd never do it, unless they nerfed our pets into uselessness, pets are supposed to be dumb and hard to control yet powerful. Its part of the double edge to the magician class.<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=465781">Master Nucci</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
